        <p class="missionParagraph1">
          <ul>
            <li>Establishing schools with specialization in science and mathematics.</li>
            <li>Introducing special high level teachers to secondary schools with a mission to raise the standard of instruction in those subjects.</li>
            <li>Conducting special workshops for teachers to improve on their knowledge and to introduce new methods of teaching the subjects.</li>
            <li>Conducting special tutorial clinics for students in those subjects utilizing suitable techniques which aid understanding.</li>
