        <h1 class="missionTitle">Motivation</h1>
        <p class="missionParagraph1">
          Nigeria has a lack of presence and participation in technological research, application, and innovation<br><br>
          All technology in Nigeria is imported.<br><br>
          Students' interest in adopting science and mathematics related majors in university is low.<br><br>
          A low percentage of students in secondary school select science and math as areas of study.</p>
